Text.string: I see ya! Bang bang. You dead.
Well, will ya look at that?
Yer all blister! Gonna pop ya!
I let my gun do the talkin'.
That shot brought a tear to my eye!
And I ain't gonna bury ya.
Let the rivers run red with the dead!
You ain't seen the last of me!
He who fights and ducks away...
That looks like some good cover!
I'll patch ya up best I can.
You look a hot mess, bot.
That looks like it hurt, brother.
That's right, I dabble in the medicines.
